1. *Pogrešio* je izveštaj za prošlu nedelju. (He has missed the report for last week.)
2. Trebalo je da *pogreši* nešto, ali on to nije učinio. (He should have missed something, but he didn't.)
3. Onaj koji je *pogrešio* je dobio kaznu. (The one who has missed it got a punishment.)
4. Ona je *pogrešila* u oceni. (She has misjudged.)
5. Ono što je *pogrešio* je bilo bitno. (What he has missed was important.)
6. *Pogrešila* je u svojim procenama. (She has made a mistake in her estimates.)